Command Terms

pip list: returns the list of packages in the current environment.

deactivate: deactivates the current environment.

souce/call: activates the specified environment.

pip install: installs specified packge.

pip freezeL outpus installed packaged in a requirements format.

pip freeze > requirements.txt creates a text file with the required packages.

pip uninstall: uninstalls specified package.

pip show: shows information about the installed package.

pip search: searches for packages.